views.text:
GM Diet is a 7 day only diet plan to quickly lose weight (up to 8Kgs!) for that perfect look boosting your confidence.

Diet consists of fruits, vegetables, dairy and grains that you any way consume in day to day life – just that the diet program organises the quantity and type of food to be taken on each day.
Check out sample diet plan for all seven days.

So what are you waiting for? – Checkout out shopping list from the information button below and get started!
What are benefits of GM Diet?

• Lose upto 8Kgs in just 7 days.
 • Cleanse and detoxify your body – feel energetic and light.
 • Glowing skin.
 • Remove fat from waist and belly.

• Mild headache: With every diet plan change, your body resists and takes a while to getting used to it. It goes away with your determination (control your cravings) and as you progress into the diet.
 • Muscle weakness: This again is a case of your body resisting to new diet during initial days. This too is temporary and goes away as you progress into the diet.

Drink plenty of water to avoid above two effects.

GM diet plan should not be followed by diabetic person, pregnant woman, breastfeeding mom, thyroid problems and during menstruation.

• Drink lots of water (minimum 14 glass).
 • Supplement diet with moderate exercise daily (walk/jog).
 • Only Green tea (without sugar/honey) allowed.
 • Strict no to alcohol or cold drink.
 • Give at least 2 weeks of break before you start GM diet again.

 Please note: Weight loss varies (range of 1-8 kgs) for individual based on age, gender, medical conditions and strictness towards following diet.

To begin with:
 • Continue eating healthy diet (fruits, vegetables).
 • Start exercise (gym/yoga). 
 • Make drinking water an habit - it does wonders!.
 • No alcohol or cold drink.
For detailed day wise diet plan, download Post-GM (PGM) diet plan

Watermelon or any other fruit replacement: Replace with any seasonal fruit. Idea is to eat only (and variety of) fruits on fruit day.

Mushroom or any other vegetable replacement: Replace it with any seasonal vegetable of your choice. Idea is to eat only (and variety of) vegetables.

Banana: Try to eat banana else Apricots or Dates or Nectarin or Figs - do remember to limit the count to around 8.

Milk: Buttermilk or low fat yogurt or almond milk. Do not add sugar.

Tomato: Try to have tomatoes in any form (soup, puree, salad) as this is a key ingredient - if at all you can not take it then replace it with any vegetable.

Tofu: Paneer or egg-white or black channa.

Rajma: Black channa or Channa daal

Brown rice: White rice but less quantity.

Try the ingredients as mentioned in app to maximize weight loss.

views.text:
• Can I drink tea/coffee during diet?
You can take only green tea (without sugar/honey).

• What are non-veg alternatives?
Please check tip for the day section for non-veg alternatives.

 • I am on medication, can I follow GM diet?
Please consult your doctor once before starting any diet.

 • Some diet items are not available, please suggest alternatives?
Refer Alternatives section above.

• Can I continue my gym/exercise?
Only light weight exercises like jogging/swimming/cardio for 30-40mins should be done.

 • I have night shift, how do I follow the diet?
Follow the diet plan in given order. So whenever you get up, drink lime water followed by breakfast item, then mid-day snack and so on.

 • Can I take protein supplements like whey?
No, any protein supplement is not recommended during the diet.

• Can I eat dry fruits?
It is not recommended during the diet.

 • How much water should I drink?
During diet, around 3.5-4lts of water.

• Should I drink water immediately after meal?
Drink water 15-20mins post meal.

 • What are herbs?
Herbs like coriander, mint leaves, oregano or chili flakes could be used.

• Please mention quantity of each item?
Check out daily shopping list for quantity by pressing i button.

 • I feel hungry during GM diet, what to do?
You can increase portion of fruits/vegetables and drink soup if you feel hungry.

 • What if I continue the diet for more than a week?
GM diet is strictly 7day diet. You can start the diet again after 2 weeks of gap.

 • What to eat after GM diet?
Please follow the steps mentioned on Page 1 of this app.

 • I am 15yrs old. Can I follow the diet?
Recommended age for GM diet is 18yrs.

• Is headache normal during diet?
Initial few day, you might experience mild headache. Drink lots of water.

 • I have got upset stomach, should I stop?
If this continues for a day, please stop the diet.

• I ate roti/rice on day2, should I continue?
Please continue to complete the diet as per plan and control your cravings.

 • Would I lose belly fat?
GM diet will help you lose overall body fat that includes belly fat.

 • Do not find your question here?
